ssets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T23:19:10.000Z","msg":"睇黎好多人都比人哄過上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望今年班Dse考生，唔會比人呃啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />曬錢曬時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc38009b2959a9ccf0c5ebb7f474711a0b386c77","tid":2472620,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T17:02:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210423/GXK5SZFT7VAEFMITCPC75PDL6Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210423%2FGXK5SZFT7VAEFMITCPC75PDL6Y%2F&d=uw8R2zILh4IVFJjxqgttXGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=5459a2bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210423%2FGXK5SZFT7VAEFMITCPC75PDL6Y%2F&h=1077d620\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210423/GXK5SZFT7VAEFMITCPC75PDL6Y/</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n社會專題：交友App搵獵物 教育移民乜都sell <br />\n「中醫妹」涉呃客買掠水療程<br />\n<br />\n疫情下美容院被數度勒令停業，疑有推銷集團伺機擴展掠水業務殺入中醫界！有「中醫妹」經交友App釣客，噓寒問暖故作曖昧，目的為𠱁客購買中醫療程，即使事主無病無痛，仍被游說幫襯逾萬元、長達一年的中醫療程，有事主指「美容院呃人就聽過，估唔到中醫都呃人。」中醫妹更會推銷其他過萬元的教育課程。記者放蛇約見「中醫妹」，直擊𠱁客過程，她們揚言「集團有中醫、西醫、醫學針劑、養生療程，乜都有」，十分落力。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：駐場醫師稱不知情 業界：絕少預繳<br />\n<br />\n近半年交友App湧現一堆「中醫妹」、「中醫仔」搵食，令不少男女成為獵物，當中不少被𠱁落叠，預繳購買昂貴中醫療程，同類以交友App撈客推銷手法，過去常用於美容或健身療程。Jacky去年12月經交友App結識女網友，數天後對方帶他到旺角一教育中心推銷投資課程，眼見他無興趣，對方便介紹另一職員Heidi給他，自此Heidi日夜關懷他的健康，不久更帶Jacky看中醫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ddMcAks-x8TDKMsoCui5kKV302o=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FBUNC3LP7JBZVESGAF2DZK4RT4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FddMcAks-x8TDKMsoCui5kKV302o%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFBUNC3LP7JBZVESGAF2DZK4RT4.jpg&h=8bfe8421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■當得知記者有意看中醫，Heidi即興奮約見面，同日帶記者約診。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n業務範圍廣 受害人易落叠<br />\n<br />\n「醫師叫我兩星期覆診一次。」Jacky憶述診症後，對方落力游說幫襯「調理身體機能」療程，「話免診金，半年要萬零蚊。」他稱是學生無力支付，對方稱可分期付款，最終他簽卡付款。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：公司董事 營商屢捲風波<br />\n<br />\n「冇病冇痛要睇半年，仲要成萬蚊。」Jacky服中藥粉一個多月後，質疑Heidi為賺佣金帶他看中醫，「美容院呃人就聽過，估唔到中醫都呃人。」最終他無力還卡數，要家人還債。<br />\n<br />\n記者其後聯絡到Heidi，她自稱。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n其間記者透露有意調理身體，她即力銷一名姓甄中醫，。。。。。。課程。<br />\n<br />\n大專生Alex亦經交友App認識中醫妹Aki，。。。。。。。。，最後因預約爆滿才逃過一劫。<br />\n<br />\n不過此前Alex已被推銷報讀投資移民課程，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/f2UWdRL9WaGMFFtKdenb5w0y2KY=/802x1069/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ESVE532LMNF3BAY4MZJKCOATJ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ff2UWdRL9WaGMFFtKdenb5w0y2KY%3D%2F802x1069%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FESVE532LMNF3BAY4MZJKCOATJ4.jpg&h=f3c8f3eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Jacky被中醫妹Heidi推銷中醫療程，終花逾萬元預付一年藥費。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6r8dcAqnnSx6RVw2E6OrcmZC-sQ=/802x1203/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/47WYDDAD3NDDZHGNWBQKLZZULY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6r8dcAqnnSx6RVw2E6OrcmZC-sQ%3D%2F802x1203%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F47WYDDAD3NDDZHGNWBQKLZZULY.jpg&h=34bd5e3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Diana自言無病無痛，卻被推銷一年療程，職員更指要「日日食先有效」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YMq9pZ63X1m8ECXiaTsn_tJwldg=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HXNG2O4EA5DOPKLDUJHOTQ3TTU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYMq9pZ63X1m8ECXiaTsn_tJwldg%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHXNG2O4EA5DOPKLDUJHOTQ3TTU.jpg&h=d8d67952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Heidi除劏客見中醫，亦會帶客到HKUE學校推銷收費逾萬元的課程。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大律師：串謀詐騙最高判監14年<br />\n<br />\n少女Diana被網名Hally的「中醫仔」誘看中醫，她指中醫僅作不足五分鐘的簡單問診，應診後職員向她展示中醫療程價目表，收費由1,300元起，建議她買為期一年逾20,000元療程，更指「日日食先有效」。Hally則附和指，「𠵱家疫情平咗。」<br />\n<br />\nDiana自覺無病痛仍被推銷一年療程，。。。。。。。「佢哋好識玩，疫情下諗到另一出路，竟然sell中醫，咁樣呃錢令我好憤怒。」<br />\n<br />\n大律師陸偉雄指，事件中如有人謊稱沒有回佣而帶客消費，或干犯欺詐，合作而知情的相關機構，包括提供服務的中醫、美容院、教育中心，亦可被控串謀詐騙，最高刑罰判監14年。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n但陸補充，需視乎其銷售手法，若對方有技巧地隱晦其回報，「例如話有coupon，已經叫表明咗（利益），咁就冇足夠證據」難以提控。"},{"pid":"a0398e556fc2054b23e7a9017332c72bbc13ad78","tid":2472620,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T17:09:51.000Z","msg":"可能佢遲啲扮黃, 又話有英國學歷就去英聯邦國家有用,<br />\n針對呢點<br />\n<br />\n1.遙距課程唔計嘅<br />\n2.加拿大移民, 香港學歷都承認"},{"pid":"beac0c1dc827ccd522c3bbb059b71d1107edadac","tid":2472620,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9370f9bb9efa9e5f4d88afb9b4067acd65ddf64","tid":2472620,"uid":394826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1bf90822c03a772c9530dc0fda20f25979b2d6b","tid":2472620,"uid":381948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T18:42:44.000Z","msg":"有個女仔係俾佢個friend叫佢入去(可能有好大仇），然後高賢個老師-miss 曾因為咁樣收唔到傭金，之後每次個女仔問呢個miss任何嘢嘅時候，個Miss都係咁Hea住答佢。<br />\n<br />\nMiss曾十大罪<br />\n某澳洲不知名大學degree出身。扮有料<br />\n上堂時候跟PowerPoint讀<br />\n吹水唔抹嘴，hard sell人話到自己間學校好勁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:09:39.000Z","msg":"我記得一開頭會叫班學生玩9型人格，懶係好人禁睇班學生既人格，事實上係知道完學生性格之後方便控制個學生，同埋用咩方法去應付個學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T17:10:50.000Z","msg":"咁搞法, 就算愛因斯坦智商, 都畀佢控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e42b07279b3192cc68c902719d4d9361a9e3665","tid":2472620,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4fa4c6d1ad0996c34cd09328d6b764a99c7259a","tid":2472620,"uid":378177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1bd8c8ac2d3be03b0a3bb21c5df540e8813055e","tid":2472620,"uid":394826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db5aa3c95ffc2958be5d8e94c33cd2c6bab31fd2","tid":2472620,"uid":378177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T01:13:20.000Z","msg":"條友好撚陰濕架頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:34:42.000Z","msg":"同埋佢懶係好好人禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講到讀ive 要用好多錢 但其實你讀完HD又會哄你讀埋上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />逼你聽個升學講座"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:19:51.000Z","msg":"佢仲講到好為我着想咁，死都逼我報左先，到時放榜就唔會咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我本身話想讀social science，不過佢根本冇聽我講咩，跟住就話social science 出路唔好，讀佢商科課程有着數。呢次應該係我唯一一次比傳銷呃嘅一次。 好在走得快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T17:12:05.000Z","msg":"同佢講, 香港國際中心都玩完啦, 仲讀金融?"},{"pid":"9037cfa7c109cedbfaf185192d11280279abc0b1","tid":2472620,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31340169904f367c653368fdedb52cf32025e624","tid":2472620,"uid":381948,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T13:54:13.000Z","msg":"千萬要小心DSE係門口那些找你做問卷嗰啲人，佢哋會用問你嘅聯絡方式，然之後，就會賣俾呢啲垃圾機構，然之後呢啲機構就會有你嘅聯繫方法。<br />\n<br />\n初頭嘅時候佢哋淨係會話想提供一啲升學資訊，就會約你出嚟去佢哋個地址，之後到咗現場就會係咁hard sell 你，佢間學校嘅課程。我同我嘅朋友仲記得佢當時sell我哋嘅時候，話保證入到八大，IVE同埋ASSO都唔需要額外嘥錢報。<br />\n<br />\n甚至佢話有實習機會點知連條毛都冇，甚至話自己間學校嘅學費比出邊Ive 同asso嘅學費平，點知到最後多謝收你年半11萬蚊。但之後發現IVE原來只係6萬蚊學費。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後佢會陪埋你去學資處然之後叫你簽咗佢地做擔保人等佢哋可以日後交學費嘅時候佢自己自動過咗俾間學校，之後如果你想quit呢間學校嘅話係冇機會去取消呢個貸款。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T17:29:11.000Z","msg":"如果冇去學資處, 係咪冇嘢?"},{"pid":"f9e85d341c71af07dbf88ac328e29e7b3f32d7ca","tid":2472620,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb1cb867bcbec809e91445dc66dbaa522babf9e3","tid":2472620,"uid":381948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"047c494c1a119ae8291c9c6c7184c295572a7575","tid":2472620,"uid":394826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:32:58.000Z","msg":"間野係尖東好細間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過係連登都見過幾次高賢商業學校既名 <br />\n我17年讀 讀讀下就無讀，然後有日叫我番去拎畢業證書，我呆撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心諗我無交學費，都有畢業證書？我諗佢係想做靚條數所以連未比學費既人都有。睇大家會唔會想讀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T18:41:45.000Z","msg":"佢哋而家搬咗去銅鑼灣同現代教育合併，細佐成倍，我去一田個廁所都冇佢咁細啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我識有人，佢讀咗一個sem之後冇讀都有證書拎。<br />\n有個女仔份份project都 chur到盡，科科distinction，到最後成績表個樣都係一樣。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:41:27.000Z","msg":"現代持續教育中心 ?"},{"pid":"a17c496705981edd6ee60a16ce5f25f1e004b1cc","tid":2472620,"uid":371511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf69ce2800a43b0555a18490577beda264747bb","tid":2472620,"uid":378177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e42b07279b3192cc68c902719d4d9361a9e3665","tid":2472620,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4fa4c6d1ad0996c34cd09328d6b764a99c7259a","tid":2472620,"uid":378177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1bd8c8ac2d3be03b0a3bb21c5df540e8813055e","tid":2472620,"uid":394826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:34:42.000Z","msg":"同埋佢懶係好好人禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講到讀ive 要用好多錢 但其實你讀完HD又會哄你讀埋上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />逼你聽個升學講座"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:19:51.000Z","msg":"佢仲講到好為我着想咁，死都逼我報左先，到時放榜就唔會咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我本身話想讀social science，不過佢根本冇聽我講咩，跟住就話social science 出路唔好，讀佢商科課程有着數。呢